# {{lb|en|grammar}} A grammatical form (often a [[verb]] form) that refers to an [[event]], [[transaction]], [[occurrence]], or object that happened (or had happened), or existed, at some time before [[now]] (the applicable reference time).
#: ''Example: "I <u>saw</u> the #5 bus across the street. I <u>didn’t</u> make it."''
