#*: ''This is a report on a study of the use of the '''past tense''' forms in the 53 Japanese samples compiled for the Louvain International Database of Spoken English Interlanguage (LINDSEI) project.''
#* '''2009''', Eric W. Vogt, ''Practice Makes Perfect: Spanish '''Past-Tense''' Verbs Up Close'', McGraw Hill, [https://books.google.com.au/books?id=gL9S7-OaV0QC&pg=PR5&dq=%22past+tense%22%7C%22past+tenses%22&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjN5vna1L_qAhUlH7kGHVTJAcIQ6AEwFXoECE0QAg#v=onepage&q=%22past%20tense%22%7C%22past%20tenses%22&f=false page v],
